lyrics:
[verse]
In this wild journey we're bound to roam
Through the shadows and the stars we'll find our home
Hand in hand, we'll dance, no need to pretend
Through the rhythm of our souls, true friendship won't bend

[chorus]
Friendship, like a flame, burning bright
Guiding us through every dark and endless night
Side by side, we'll conquer every twist and bend
Forever bonded, our spirits will transcend
